@NODE "Installation" "Installation"

Below are the instructions for installing these tracks onto a hard-disk. Having no call to install extra levels onto floppy
discs, I don't know how to do it. Sorry, but I'm sure you can figure it out.

So, simply copy all the files from the Backgrounds, Tiles, Worlds, Layouts, Gradients, Objects and Tracks drawers accompanying this guide
into the corresponding drawers in your XTR drawer (you'll have to select the Show All Files option for this window to drag-and-drop files). Please be sure to copy all the files across, as I'm not sure if the tracks will work without everything being present.
